{{Italic title}} {{Taxobox | image_caption = | name = ''Bellilinea'' | regnum = [[Bacterium|Bacteria]] | phylum = [[Chloroflexi (phylum)|Chloroflexi]] | classis = [[Anaerolineae]] | ordo = [[Anaerolineales]] | familia = [[Anaerolineaceae]] | genus = '''''Bellilinea''''' | genus_authority = Yamada et al. 2007<ref name=Bellilinea>{{cite journal|last1=Parte|first1=A.C.|title=Bellilinea|journal=www.bacterio.net|url=http://www.bacterio.net/bellilinea.html}}</ref> | type_species = ''Bellilinea caldifistulae''<ref name=Bellilinea/> |subdivision_ranks = [[Species]] |subdivision =''[[Bellilinea caldifistulae|B. caldifistulae]]''<ref name=Bellilinea/> }}
'''''Bellilinea''''' is a [[thermophilic]] bacteria genus from the family of [[Anaerolineaceae]] with one known species (''[[Bellilinea caldifistulae]]'').<ref name=Bellilinea/><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Parker|first1=Charles Thomas|last2=Osier|first2=Nicole Danielle|last3=Garrity|first3=George M|title=Nomenclature Abstract for Bellilinea Yamada et al. 2007.|journal=The NamesforLife Abstracts|doi=10.1601/nm.11421|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Bellilinea|journal=www.uniprot.org|url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/475960|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Yamada|first1=T|last2=Imachi|first2=H|last3=Ohashi|first3=A|last4=Harada|first4=H|last5=Hanada|first5=S|last6=Kamagata|first6=Y|last7=Sekiguchi|first7=Y|title=Bellilinea caldifistulae gen. nov., sp. nov. and Longilinea arvoryzae gen. nov., sp. nov., strictly anaerobic, filamentous bacteria of the phylum Chloroflexi isolated from methanogenic propionate-degrading consortia.|journal=International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionary Microbiology|date=October 2007|volume=57|issue=Pt 10|pages=2299–306|doi=10.1099/ijs.0.65098-0|pmid=17911301}}</ref> ''Bellilinea caldifistulae'' has been isolated from thermophilic digester sludge from [[Nagaoka, Niigata|Niigata]] in [[Japan]].<ref>{{cite journal|title=Details: DSM-17877|journal=www.dsmz.de|url=https://www.dsmz.de/catalogues/details/culture/DSM-17877.html|language=en}}</ref>
